imdb.plot outline: Hollyscoop is a weekly half-hour entertainment news Television show based on a very popular pop culture and entertainment news website Hollyscoop.com. Created for both the domestic and international markets, Hollyscoop will bring its viewers the latest in celebrity news, film, television, style, hot spots and fashion. Hollyscoop is also known for breaking international entertainment news with daily Hollyscoop exclusives.
imdb.title: Hollyscoop
plot: Entertainment news covering the biggest celebrities, red carpets, latest trends, upcoming movies and more.::Raymond Attipa
